--- a/rest-api-spec/src/yamlRestTest/resources/rest-api-spec/test/search.vectors/70_dense_vector_telemetry.yml
+++ b/rest-api-spec/src/yamlRestTest/resources/rest-api-spec/test/search.vectors/70_dense_vector_telemetry.yml
@@ -18,11 +18,6 @@ setup:
                 dims: 768
                 index: true
                 similarity: l2_norm

-                index_options:
-                  type: hnsw
-                  m: 16
-                  ef_construction: 100
               vector2:
                 type: dense_vector
                 dims: 1024

           capabilities:
             - "verbose-dense-vector-mapping-stats"
       reason: "Capability required to run test"
+
+  - do:
+      indices.delete:
+        index: index1

+      indices.create:
+        index: index1

+          settings:
+            index.number_of_shards: 2
+          mappings:
+            properties:
+              vector1:
+                type: dense_vector
+                dims: 768
+                index: true
+                similarity: l2_norm
+                element_type: byte
+                index_options:
+                  type: hnsw
+                  m: 16
+                  ef_construction: 100
+              vector2:
+                type: dense_vector
+                dims: 1024
+                index: true
+                similarity: dot_product
+              vector3:
+                type: dense_vector
+                dims: 100
+                index: false
+
   - do: { cluster.stats: { } }
   - length: { indices.mappings.field_types: 1 }
   - match: { indices.mappings.field_types.0.name: dense_vector }
